µC1Ghandy: Was the amateurish presentation of the "Demo Dienstag" in NBC Giga supportive or harmful for the purposes of your society?

µC8µC8Poti: As far as I can remember at this time our society wasn't even found. But afterwards I'd assess it more positively: Last but not least most people watching this show did like the presentation. This has shown us that the subject "demoscene" is thoroughly interesting for this target group and that it's worth for us to go into the publicity.




µC1Ghandy: Poti, much thanks for this interview!

